<div class="caption p"><p>Incarceration Status and Hospitalization Rates Within 30 Days and 90 Days After Release by Patient Characteristics in the Matched Cohort of Medicare Beneficiaries</p></div>
<div class="tbl-box p" tabindex="0"><table class="content" frame="hsides" rules="rows">
<thead>
<tr>
<th rowspan="2" align="left" valign="bottom" colspan="1">Description</th>
<th colspan="3" align="center" valign="top" rowspan="1">30 Days</th>
<th colspan="3" align="center" valign="top" rowspan="1">90 Days</th>
</tr>
<tr>
<th align="left" valign="top" rowspan="1" colspan="1">Description</th>
<th align="center" valign="top" rowspan="1" colspan="1">Never Incarcerated, % (n=110419)</th>
<th align="center" valign="top" rowspan="1" colspan="1">Released From Correctional Facility, % (n=110419)</th>
<th align="center" valign="top" rowspan="1" colspan="1">
